# why react
It's composable
It's declaritive 
    Declaritive - what should be done ? - Just tell me what to do and I'll worry about how I get it done
    Imperitive - How it should be done ? - Describe to me every step on how to do something, and I will do it

It's hirable
It's Activly maintained by skilled people

